high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the white shelves.
Pick the gold vase up from the shelf.
Move to the right and face the safe on the floor.
Put the gold vase in the safe and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a vase in a safe.

high_descs: Turn around to your left then head to the shelf beside the sofa
Pick up the yellow vase under the shelf
Turn around then head to the vault on your left
Open the vault then put in the vase then close it
anns.task_desc: Put the vase in the vault

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to the white book shelf; the one that is sitting to the immediate right of the couch.
Pick up the golden vase that is sitting on the bottom shelf of the book shelf
Turn around and walk to the white safe that is on your left, past the book shelf.  Turn left to face the white safe
Open the safe and place the vase inside the safe then close the door
anns.task_desc: Place a vase in a safe.
